    "faqTitleHighlight": "Questions",
    "faq1Q": "Does it work offline?",
    "faq1A": "Yes! The app works offline and syncs automatically when you reconnect. Perfect for job sites without Wi-Fi.",
    "faq2Q": "Is it hard to use?",
    "faq2A": "No! Obra Certa was built to be used one-handed, right on the job site. Big buttons, simple interface, no hassle.",
