    "faq3A": "Yes, any type of project! From a bathroom renovation to a high-end condo. The system adapts to your project.",
    "faq4Q": "How does the billing and technical retention system work?",
    "faq4A": "You set the labor contract value per phase or item in the schedule. At each billing, enter the percentage completed and the system automatically calculates the gross value, deducts pending advances, and applies technical retention (default 5%, but you can customize). The result is the exact net amount to pay, no surprises.",
